lead_paragraph: HSIA--Sven Erik. Holland Lodge No. 8 F&AM acknowledges with deep regret the death of our brother on February 13, 2016. Our sincere condolences are extended to his entire family. John R. Weber, Master James W. McGovern, Secretary 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  HSIA, SVEN ERIK
